{{USEflag|package=sys-apps/fwupd}}

The above list of USE flag is not comprehensive. Use {{c|equery}} (part of {{Package|app-portage/gentoolkit}}) for a full list:

{{Cmd|equery uses sys-apps/fwupd}}


== Usage ==

<code>fwupd.service</code> is launched through [[systemd]] via [[D-Bus]] automatically whenever it is needed.

Get help on what <code>fwupd</code> can do:

{{Cmd|fwupdmgr help}}


List detected and supported devices. When the device is [https://fwupd.org/lvfs/devicelist listed] but not displayed, a plugin (e.g. the <code>uefi</code> useflag) is missing.
{{Cmd|fwupdmgr get-devices}}

Refresh metadata from remote server
{{Cmd|fwupdmgr refresh}}

Check available updates for your devices:
{{Cmd|fwupdmgr get-updates}}

Install updates:
{{Cmd|fwupdmgr update}}
